{"tid":754786,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有個唔生性老豆可以點做？ 文長慎入","createTime":"2018-07-24T16:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T04:57:38.000Z","uid":150840,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a353feff8a7f1f0557d74dac94d43ad31b2d4d73","tid":754786,"uid":150840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:18:08.000Z","msg":"文長<br />\n<br />\n有個爛賭老豆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾個月前因為腎衰竭末期入院<br />\n<br />\n講返背景<br />\n窮，毒，獨子 公屋撚 無錢<br />\n母親同佢就離左婚<br />\n<br />\n佢有呢個病 我同母親都關心佢<br />\n但始終離左婚 母親間唔中會同佢出去行街食飯 睇戲<br />\n就唔會係屋企住既<br />\n我就平時要返工 佢無野做 我開支都多左<br />\n<br />\n佢宜家學識左係屋企洗肚 <br />\n每日洗三次  都算唔太差 <br />\n起碼洗完肚佢仲可以去樓下行下街<br />\n我都叫佢得閒報下d濕鳩班識下朋友仔<br />\n<br />\n但係佢終覺我同母親唔陪佢 <br />\n話咩日日係屋企好孤獨<br />\n落街又好似流浪漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔知可以點 唔通唔返工日日食空氣陪佢咩<br />\n<br />\n盡管多d打電話關心佢<br />\n收工買飯比佢（比佢d飯錢用黎賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n但佢仲係變本加厲<br />\n<br />\n點變本加厲法？<br />\n真係好心累 岩岩醫院打黎又話佢入左院啦<br />\n<br />\n佢宜家隔唔夠一個星期就會扮野入院<br />\n仲要傷害自己身體。務求 真實<br />\n唔食野 等血糖低 自己call白車<br />\n係街飲酒暈低 等途人送入醫院<br />\n<br />\n你話係咪痴線<br />\n入左院為求住得耐d<br />\n仲要扮精神病係咁鬧醫生姑娘<br />\n或者狂掉野落地下（其實我覺得佢已經有少少精神病，但醫院check過話無）<br />\n<br />\n我問點解要咁做<br />\n佢話係醫院有好多人陪<br />\n同埋有姑娘餵佢食飯<br />\n..<br />\n我真係比佢迫到就顛<br />\n母親直頭話由佢死<br />\n<br />\n佢今個月已經入左三次醫院<br />\n計埋之前已經入左差唔多十幾次醫院<br />\n<br />\n已經將我對佢嘅耐性漸漸磨滅<br />\n我都唔知佢邊次係真病定假病<br />\n<br />\n可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5611c67ff2bae4f6bc33c427aee8097c1b12f5","tid":754786,"uid":41737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:19:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d269b968ae9f6e5ce8831230ca8b477f776d5fdb","tid":754786,"uid":88428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:19:47.000Z","msg":"買部ipad 教佢睇av"},{"pid":"75896c3015a5911b4040a1cfbcf25fcb44b98e02","tid":754786,"uid":145923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:22:02.000Z","msg":"由得佢啦.你已經做左你既責任.條路佢自己揀.由得佢自己受."},{"pid":"232285295ada4310b969415917dae496d2fe27e3","tid":754786,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:23:12.000Z","msg":"再係咁<br />\n你都有精神衰弱"},{"pid":"19f4455b4b3498740f3cdde3c1af05f887a7f9d0","tid":754786,"uid":150840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d5611c67ff2bae4f6bc33c427aee8097c1b12f5","tid":754786,"uid":41737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:19:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:25:08.000Z","msg":"嘗試緊 唉<br />\n<br />\n我平時返工佢會call爆我叫我去醫院睇佢<br />\n仲要買d咩炒飯至類比佢<br />\n<br />\n上次去探佢 <br />\n因為佢踢醫生比人綁住左<br />\n姑娘餵佢餵飯（仲要幾靚女）<br />\n我望見佢個樣真係呢<br />\n梗住姑娘叫我餵返 又係到扮可憐<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚嬲  點解要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5272056ec68a1826c880ebd24a17839d52d2f7bc","tid":754786,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:25:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f41fcb1838e462b381470b0042f5967a71a393ab","tid":754786,"uid":150840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d269b968ae9f6e5ce8831230ca8b477f776d5fdb","tid":754786,"uid":88428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:19:47.000Z","msg":"買部ipad 教佢睇av"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:26:07.000Z","msg":"睇av都無用 你估佢係屋企無睇<br />\n咁大年紀咩都睇過哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71840f1ee864fe907ebd6a2967d9c4bb0338ee8a","tid":754786,"uid":150840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75896c3015a5911b4040a1cfbcf25fcb44b98e02","tid":754786,"uid":145923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:22:02.000Z","msg":"由得佢啦.你已經做左你既責任.條路佢自己揀.由得佢自己受."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:27:48.000Z","msg":"今次係我第一次收到醫院電話<br />\n無飛的過去 無打比佢<br />\n<br />\n但始終老豆得一個<br />\n都係好撚心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽日仲要返早工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0bb43e718d5b9ae451fa39344ff41b5e3312ff","tid":754786,"uid":150840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"232285295ada4310b969415917dae496d2fe27e3","tid":754786,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:23:12.000Z","msg":"再係咁<br />\n你都有精神衰弱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:28:43.000Z","msg":"我覺得我宜家已經有<br />\n真係好撚無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1a18e9aed84ea995882ac0041e9c161cc36f56","tid":754786,"uid":44878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:33:47.000Z","msg":"道德爭議無分對錯：人不為己，天誅地滅<br />\n天生邊個家庭冇得揀，後天自己的路自己揀<br />\n<br />\n依刻你老豆長期病患都算，仲要拖後腿雪上加霜<br />\n完全無企係你同前妻既角度諗過<br />\n咁撚自私既人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死不足惜</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8876d76045300a443ba9509f0bc5805ab5c2277c","tid":754786,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc01bcfa026a34b12bae2b2ceddf2e45aeae0840","tid":754786,"uid":122996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:37:02.000Z","msg":"老豆係得一個，血緣呢樣嘢真係割裂唔開嘅。<br />\n但係你嘅人生都係得一次，佢而家係濫用緊你對佢嘅關心同愛。影響緊好多你嘅生活。<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫你唔好再關心佢，但嘗試下俾佢知你嘅痛同苦惱。<br />\n睇下佢有咩回應。<br />\n不過都真係有可能，情緒出現問題令佢渴求關注嘅。<br />\n咁就要及早搵專業人士幫手啦。"},{"pid":"a5999238eeaa9f5164b37067ebe7ed12addd91b4","tid":754786,"uid":150840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T16:48:04.000Z","msg":"好羨慕其他人有個正常老豆<br />\n我唔求咩父幹母幹<br />\n起碼有手有腳打份普通工夠養自去己<br />\n<br />\n佢病淨係想佢多d正面能量<br />\n唔好咁負面<br />\n係我返工嘅時候可以識照顧自己<br />\n<br />\n點解到頭來要咁自私對我<br />\n今日屋企又得返我一個<br />\n<br />\n而佢又選擇又扮野入院<br />\n我都已經早d放工諗住同佢一齊食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19cc101d80c831cb4020972f80d7ae00b659c11","tid":754786,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:35:22.000Z","msg":"比個擁抱樓主。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd885c97cf612b0f71d897fbfd81cdbfcac4af7","tid":754786,"uid":180948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T17:48:59.000Z","msg":"哈哈 同我屋企有啲似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9221a43094a7a4c43f07b39b70fd1394697802","tid":754786,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T01:32:44.000Z","msg":"不是人來 唔好理佢啦"},{"pid":"40e034089c118a0a155bfc4b71f0ed2dc01b1639","tid":754786,"uid":194069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:40:56.000Z","msg":"唔係一句佢係你老豆你就可以比佢綑綁住你人生，你越係咁縱容佢呢d無理嘅行為佢只會得寸進尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下好認真同佢講下自己感受之後頭也不回咁離開啦，擔心老豆健康嘅，可以私底下同醫生傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打加油 你絕對係一個好男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8baafe83f9b1c79f62173027888bda9efa413bd","tid":754786,"uid":38341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:47:34.000Z","msg":"好明白樓主 <br />\n我都有一個咁嘅老豆<br />\n玩到一日入一次院<br />\nD姑娘就認得佢 : 呀伯!又係你呀? <br />\n照顧佢真係好心力交瘁!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b2afd5e534de2191f2963f05b87dd08be61c97","tid":754786,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:51:10.000Z","msg":"唔好話扮精神病，佢真係有抑鬱都唔奇<br />\n叫醫院轉介佢去精神科"},{"pid":"f9638e0b6bfd09c1ba9251a3fbba04aa57b4b7a8","